WEBVTT

00:19.720 --> 00:22.840
BAXIA MANOR

00:24.200 --> 00:27.080
Do not hurt my mother.

00:27.160 --> 00:29.280
Do not hurt my mother.

00:30.920 --> 00:32.720
Hurt my mother.

00:33.800 --> 00:35.200
Do not…

00:36.400 --> 00:38.080
-Do not…
-Give me the food box.

00:38.720 --> 00:40.560
-Yes.
-Wait outside.

00:40.640 --> 00:41.720
Yes.

00:41.800 --> 00:44.320
Do not… hurt…

00:45.120 --> 00:46.400
my mother.

00:49.280 --> 00:51.680
-Young Master, please do not be afraid.
-Do not

00:51.760 --> 00:54.160
-hurt my mother.
-I brought you something to eat.

00:55.240 --> 00:56.080
Hurt…

00:56.160 --> 00:57.680
Your mother is safe.

00:58.360 --> 00:59.320
You need not worry.

00:59.840 --> 01:01.600
Come, have a little.

01:01.680 --> 01:04.720
Do not hurt my mother.

01:05.519 --> 01:07.920
Hurt my mother.

01:08.960 --> 01:09.840
Do not…

01:09.920 --> 01:10.880
Young Master,

01:10.960 --> 01:14.120
you have barely eaten or drunk
for days now.

01:14.800 --> 01:16.000
If you go on like this,

01:16.080 --> 01:18.600
your body will not hold up.

01:18.680 --> 01:21.880
Do not hurt my mother.

01:24.760 --> 01:25.840
Do not…

01:25.920 --> 01:27.400
Young Master,

01:28.000 --> 01:29.400
if you refuse to eat,

01:29.480 --> 01:32.440
how will you find the strength
to protect your mother?

01:47.360 --> 01:49.480
Slow down. There is more.

02:03.280 --> 02:04.520
My little master!

02:05.360 --> 02:06.680
You cannot do that.

02:06.760 --> 02:07.600
You cannot.

02:07.680 --> 02:08.800
That is ink!

02:08.880 --> 02:10.440
You must not eat it.

02:11.320 --> 02:13.560
You must not.

02:13.640 --> 02:15.680
What are we to do?

02:21.600 --> 02:24.280
A single maid's death
frightened him into illness?

02:25.720 --> 02:26.840
Have you forgotten?

02:27.920 --> 02:29.640
I survived the fire at the Eastern Palace

02:29.720 --> 02:30.920
when I was his age.

02:32.000 --> 02:35.560
Young Master was raised
away from Your Highness.

02:35.640 --> 02:38.720
He has not inherited your courage.

02:38.800 --> 02:40.200
A small shock

02:40.280 --> 02:43.240
is enough to unnerve him.

02:43.320 --> 02:46.520
If this continues,

02:46.600 --> 02:48.920
I fear he may truly fall gravely ill.

02:51.680 --> 02:52.560
And so?

02:53.800 --> 02:56.600
So… I humbly suggest

02:56.680 --> 02:58.440
finding him a companion.

02:59.160 --> 03:03.640
Perhaps it may steady his spirit.

03:05.160 --> 03:06.040
Whom do you propose?

03:07.600 --> 03:09.640
I heard from Xun

03:10.320 --> 03:13.600
that Madam was close
to the Fan family back in Lin'an.

03:13.680 --> 03:14.680
They were good friends.

03:15.360 --> 03:18.400
The Fan family's youngest daughter
is presently in our residence.

03:18.480 --> 03:19.480
Perhaps she might--

03:27.960 --> 03:29.480
Since you have thought it through,

03:30.000 --> 03:31.400
go ask Yuanqing for the girl.

03:32.640 --> 03:33.480
Yes.

04:18.120 --> 04:20.519
Little girl, do not be afraid.

04:21.079 --> 04:22.760
Nanny is taking you to meet someone.

04:44.960 --> 04:46.200
Young Master.

04:46.760 --> 04:48.760
Set the brush down for a moment.

04:50.440 --> 04:53.280
Young Master, look.
See who I have brought.

04:59.760 --> 05:01.240
Yu Bao'er.

05:36.360 --> 05:38.080
Yu Bao'er.

05:45.960 --> 05:46.800
Here.

05:59.800 --> 06:01.560
It is alright, Bao'er.

06:01.640 --> 06:03.280
I know you want a good cry,

06:03.360 --> 06:04.440
but wipe those tears.

06:07.240 --> 06:09.320
I am here now. I will protect you.

06:11.480 --> 06:12.600
It is alright.

06:13.200 --> 06:15.240
I will keep you safe.

06:19.440 --> 06:20.760
Take this.

06:21.360 --> 06:24.760
If you are ever in danger, blow it.

06:24.840 --> 06:26.800
Someone will come for you.

06:28.200 --> 06:30.160
Really?

06:31.560 --> 06:32.600
Really.

06:35.760 --> 06:37.960
Once, I fell into a well.

06:38.040 --> 06:39.760
I shouted until my voice gave out.

06:39.840 --> 06:41.400
When Father found me,

06:41.480 --> 06:43.520
I could not even speak.

06:43.600 --> 06:46.280
After that, he carved me
this bamboo whistle.

06:46.360 --> 06:47.600
Once you blow it,

06:47.680 --> 06:49.320
someone will come.

06:50.000 --> 06:51.240
It truly works.

06:52.200 --> 06:54.360
I… I need to tell you.

06:54.440 --> 06:57.400
These past few days, he…

06:57.480 --> 06:59.640
he took a stick that big

06:59.720 --> 07:01.200
and struck her with it.

07:01.280 --> 07:03.760
Again and again. There was blood.

07:03.840 --> 07:05.360
I did not dare look.

08:33.720 --> 08:37.039
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

08:45.920 --> 08:47.520
Everyone assemble!

08:50.720 --> 08:52.000
All of you, out!

08:52.080 --> 08:53.600
-Line up!
-Out!

08:54.640 --> 08:55.800
On your feet!

08:56.560 --> 08:57.560
-On your feet!
-Move!

08:57.640 --> 08:59.120
Out! Form up!

08:59.200 --> 09:00.280
Out, out, out!

09:01.200 --> 09:02.080
Faster!

09:02.160 --> 09:04.280
-Line up!
-Take one tool each!

09:04.360 --> 09:06.080
-Move!
-Time to work!

09:06.160 --> 09:07.360
Take your tools!

09:07.440 --> 09:08.640
Come on. Let's move!

09:08.720 --> 09:10.760
Take one tool each! Move it!

09:11.800 --> 09:13.440
Out to quarry stone and repair the road!

09:15.320 --> 09:16.240
Miss.

09:16.760 --> 09:17.600
Out! Form up!

09:18.240 --> 09:19.120
Move, move!

09:19.200 --> 09:20.680
Until we verify who you are,

09:20.760 --> 09:22.480
you are not permitted to leave.

09:22.560 --> 09:23.920
If you are a law-abiding citizen,

09:24.000 --> 09:25.280
then obey the rules.

09:26.520 --> 09:28.400
I have already sent word to Jizhou.

09:29.040 --> 09:30.840
Once your identity is confirmed,
you may go.

09:31.880 --> 09:33.000
Until then,

09:33.080 --> 09:34.880
quarry stone for the road.
Earn your meal here.

09:35.800 --> 09:36.720
Move, move!

09:37.440 --> 09:38.480
Out! Form up!

09:42.160 --> 09:43.360
Up on your feet!

09:44.040 --> 09:45.160
Time to work!

09:48.880 --> 09:49.960
Move, move!

09:50.040 --> 09:50.960
Out!

09:53.480 --> 09:54.720
No more lying around!

09:56.440 --> 09:57.480
One tool each!

09:57.560 --> 09:58.400
Hurry up!

10:00.680 --> 10:02.120
Out! Form up!

10:04.520 --> 10:05.480
Got your tools?

10:06.400 --> 10:07.520
Listen up!

10:08.320 --> 10:09.800
Pairs of two!

10:09.880 --> 10:11.760
Head to the back hills and dig stone!

10:12.280 --> 10:14.680
Ten large baskets for men!

10:15.280 --> 10:18.040
Fifteen small baskets for women!

10:18.120 --> 10:19.240
That earns you one meal!

10:20.680 --> 10:22.760
Zhang the mason, let's team up today.

10:22.840 --> 10:25.680
Madam Li, we'll pair up.

10:26.440 --> 10:28.400
That new girl's thin as a twig.

10:28.480 --> 10:29.840
She clearly can't lift up a thing.

10:29.920 --> 10:31.040
I'm not teaming with her.

10:31.120 --> 10:32.440
Find someone strong.

10:34.040 --> 10:37.480
-Sir, you and me.
-Follow me. I promise you won't go hungry.

10:37.560 --> 10:38.640
Yes, we'll pair up.

10:38.720 --> 10:39.760
We'll team up in a bit.

10:42.080 --> 10:43.720
If you pair with this old fellow,

10:44.440 --> 10:46.600
we'll make it easier on you.

10:46.680 --> 10:48.200
Ten small baskets will do.

10:49.240 --> 10:50.160
That's a bargain.

10:51.800 --> 10:52.840
I'll carry for you.

10:53.880 --> 10:56.560
I may be old, but I still have my dignity.

10:56.640 --> 10:59.520
How could I let a young woman
bear my load?

11:00.160 --> 11:02.560
I can dig ten baskets myself.

11:03.880 --> 11:05.880
No way.

11:05.960 --> 11:07.240
Miss.

11:07.320 --> 11:09.720
The old man Tao is peculiar.

11:09.800 --> 11:12.000
All day long, he spouts bookish nonsense.

11:12.080 --> 11:14.240
No one understands him. Pay him no mind.

11:17.520 --> 11:18.360
Move out!

11:20.120 --> 11:22.120
Let's go!

11:23.080 --> 11:24.400
Sir, let me steady you.

11:26.080 --> 11:27.400
Keep up!

11:28.040 --> 11:29.600
The new girl's not bad.

11:31.760 --> 11:33.040
I'll carry your hoe for you.

11:33.120 --> 11:34.040
Keep up!

11:34.840 --> 11:37.080
Let's get to work!

11:37.160 --> 11:38.400
Work, work!

11:51.000 --> 11:52.080
‎Be careful.

12:01.640 --> 12:02.480
Careful!

12:05.160 --> 12:06.000
Sir,

12:06.640 --> 12:07.880
at that pace,

12:08.440 --> 12:09.480
you haven't eaten in days?

12:10.520 --> 12:11.360
Let me help.

12:12.280 --> 12:14.280
I can manage. Step aside.

12:16.200 --> 12:17.400
Come here.

12:18.840 --> 12:20.160
Mind your footing!

12:20.240 --> 12:22.760
Where did you get such strength?

12:25.800 --> 12:28.440
You speak like a scholar.

12:28.520 --> 12:30.360
What are you doing here with stones?

12:30.440 --> 12:32.480
I came to the border to seek my disciple.

12:32.560 --> 12:34.560
Heavy rains trapped me overnight.

12:34.640 --> 12:35.880
Before I could depart,

12:35.960 --> 12:37.880
the soldiers detained me.

12:37.960 --> 12:40.520
It must be Wei Yigui meddling in between.

12:40.600 --> 12:42.800
That unworthy son of a man.

12:43.880 --> 12:45.040
Who is Wei Yigui?

12:45.120 --> 12:47.120
The current Chancellor. Wei Yan.

12:53.320 --> 12:55.040
Less chatter! Back to work!

12:55.120 --> 12:57.040
-May I ask you something else?
-Ask.

12:58.760 --> 13:00.040
What does unworthy son mean?

13:02.320 --> 13:03.480
You have not studied?

13:04.440 --> 13:06.240
A little. Not much.

13:07.400 --> 13:09.040
Why should I be the one to teach you?

13:09.920 --> 13:10.800
Then forget it.

13:29.800 --> 13:30.640
You…

13:31.920 --> 13:34.080
Without rules, nothing stands.
Queue properly.

13:35.280 --> 13:36.640
Old man, move aside.

13:36.720 --> 13:39.080
We need to eat and get back to earning.

13:39.720 --> 13:41.800
At your age, how much can you even carry?

13:41.880 --> 13:42.840
Go home and rest.

13:42.920 --> 13:43.760
You…

13:43.840 --> 13:45.000
You rude whelp!

13:45.080 --> 13:47.200
A yapping dog with no manners!

13:47.280 --> 13:50.320
-What? You call me a dog?
-So you do understand words.

13:52.000 --> 13:53.600
Good!

13:53.680 --> 13:55.000
Well done!

13:59.600 --> 14:00.720
A girl like you,

14:00.800 --> 14:02.040
want a fight?

14:02.120 --> 14:03.640
What's happening here?

14:03.720 --> 14:05.000
He cut the line.

14:05.600 --> 14:06.720
Sun Zhuangzhuang!

14:06.800 --> 14:09.720
Built like a bull and still cutting ahead?
Back of the line!

14:11.520 --> 14:13.360
-Fine.
-Move it!

14:14.840 --> 14:15.800
Everyone line up properly!

14:20.160 --> 14:21.000
Here.

14:30.840 --> 14:32.440
Why are you staring at me like that?

14:32.520 --> 14:33.400
Is there a bun stuck to my face?

14:43.600 --> 14:45.200
You're full of learning.

14:45.840 --> 14:47.840
What are you doing here hauling rocks?

14:48.560 --> 14:50.520
Living on coarse grain
does not offend you?

14:51.120 --> 14:53.400
In this whole camp,
at least you have some discernment.

14:54.520 --> 14:55.520
The moment I reached Jizhou,

14:55.600 --> 14:58.760
I heard that rascal had disappeared again.

14:59.280 --> 15:01.960
I meant to go to Chongzhou
to look for him.

15:02.840 --> 15:03.920
Instead,

15:04.000 --> 15:05.320
I escaped the tiger's den,

15:06.160 --> 15:08.400
only to fall into the wolf's lair.

15:08.920 --> 15:11.240
Who's this rascal? Your son?

15:11.880 --> 15:13.480
Half a son.

15:14.400 --> 15:15.240
Son-in-law then.

15:18.240 --> 15:19.640
You're really an uneducated,

15:19.720 --> 15:22.440
naive girl out of nowhere.

15:22.520 --> 15:23.880
He is my disciple.

15:30.680 --> 15:32.000
My husband

15:32.760 --> 15:34.160
used to be half of a scholar too.

15:35.080 --> 15:39.080
He never got the chance
to teach me before he left.

15:40.080 --> 15:42.640
So young and already widowed.

15:42.720 --> 15:44.360
I am sorry for your loss.

15:44.440 --> 15:45.280
My condolences.

15:45.920 --> 15:47.520
Who says I am widowed?

15:47.600 --> 15:49.080
He went to war.

15:49.160 --> 15:50.280
His martial skills are excellent.

15:50.360 --> 15:53.360
You spoke as if he were dead.

16:00.560 --> 16:01.440
He had better not be.

16:06.160 --> 16:07.000
Early spring is still bitter.

16:08.080 --> 16:09.880
You'll catch a cold. Put this on.

16:10.480 --> 16:11.360
No need.

16:18.240 --> 16:20.960
Two months stuck in this cursed place,
eating nothing but gruel.

16:21.040 --> 16:23.760
First time I have seen
such a pretty little thing.

16:25.280 --> 16:26.840
Stop pairing with that old relic.

16:26.920 --> 16:27.800
Come with us.

16:27.880 --> 16:30.160
We will see that you eat well.

16:31.280 --> 16:32.760
-That is right.
-Utter nonsense!

16:33.480 --> 16:34.960
Have you no decency?

16:35.520 --> 16:37.200
Old though I am,

16:37.280 --> 16:39.520
I will not allow such insolence!

16:39.600 --> 16:41.760
-Who dares step forward?
-Move aside.

16:41.840 --> 16:43.440
Out of the way, old man.

16:44.440 --> 16:45.880
Stop waving that stick around.

16:45.960 --> 16:47.600
I have seen plenty of thugs.

16:47.680 --> 16:49.880
But men who prey on the elderly?

16:49.960 --> 16:51.040
That is a new low.

16:51.840 --> 16:53.440
There are no officers here.

16:53.520 --> 16:55.080
I could break this old man in half.

16:55.160 --> 16:56.120
You would not dare!

16:56.200 --> 16:57.200
Yes, I would.

16:57.280 --> 16:59.080
-Watch me.
-Come at me if you dare.

17:11.560 --> 17:12.400
Jin.

17:12.480 --> 17:14.400
There is such a thing as first claim.

17:14.480 --> 17:16.079
I saw her first.

17:16.839 --> 17:18.200
Do not try to take what is mine.

17:19.640 --> 17:21.520
You fool.

17:22.079 --> 17:23.720
I am saving your life.

17:23.800 --> 17:25.800
I have no wish to bury you.

17:26.319 --> 17:27.760
Is that not right, Mrs. Fan?

17:28.800 --> 17:30.560
Mr. Jin…

17:33.760 --> 17:34.960
You dare lay a hand on her?

17:35.040 --> 17:36.280
Beat him!

17:36.360 --> 17:37.280
Hit him!

17:37.360 --> 17:39.120
-Hit him!
-Stop fighting!

17:40.360 --> 17:41.800
What is going on here?

17:41.880 --> 17:43.280
You four, come with me!

17:43.360 --> 17:44.920
Send them to the front lines!

17:45.000 --> 17:46.520
-Stop crying. Go!
-Come on.

17:48.080 --> 17:49.760
Do not leave me behind!

17:49.840 --> 17:51.000
I'm still here!

17:51.080 --> 17:52.360
We forgot Tao!

17:53.600 --> 17:54.440
Careful.

17:54.520 --> 17:56.080
-Stop right there!
-Slow down.

17:56.160 --> 17:57.640
Do not shake these old bones apart!

17:57.720 --> 17:58.760
Move it!

18:14.880 --> 18:17.400
Tonight, we'll come find you.

18:17.480 --> 18:18.480
Listen for the cat.

18:53.920 --> 18:55.720
WOMEN'S QUARTERS

19:21.000 --> 19:22.040
-Come.
-Let's go.

19:27.120 --> 19:28.720
It's about to rain. Where are we going?

19:28.800 --> 19:30.160
Don't ask. Just follow me.

19:36.920 --> 19:39.240
Someone is coming. The fire. The fire!

19:58.480 --> 19:59.960
All right. They are gone.

20:00.040 --> 20:00.880
Light it.

20:04.840 --> 20:05.720
How is this place?

20:06.280 --> 20:08.360
If there is something to discuss,
we meet here.

20:11.680 --> 20:13.840
No wonder you get things done, Yuanbao.

20:18.800 --> 20:21.760
What is all this? There is so much.

20:25.280 --> 20:26.280
Wait.

20:27.840 --> 20:29.720
-This is my mother's.
-What?

20:29.800 --> 20:30.760
How is it here?

20:46.640 --> 20:48.080
This is my sister's.

20:48.160 --> 20:50.120
I gave it to her

20:50.200 --> 20:51.760
for her birthday.

20:51.840 --> 20:52.920
She loved it.

20:53.520 --> 20:55.000
Carried it everywhere.

20:56.560 --> 20:57.680
Used it all the time.

21:02.240 --> 21:03.840
How did it get here?

21:05.080 --> 21:06.040
What happened?

21:15.760 --> 21:16.600
Changyu?

21:16.680 --> 21:17.960
There was a disaster.

21:20.000 --> 21:21.600
Lin'an was slaughtered by bandits.

21:24.280 --> 21:25.400
Constable Wang.

21:26.720 --> 21:28.240
Mrs. Yin from the noodle stall.

21:29.200 --> 21:30.280
Chef Li.

21:31.440 --> 21:33.000
The inn boys from Yixiang Restaurant.

21:34.120 --> 21:35.240
Kang.

21:36.560 --> 21:38.520
The villagers in Xigu Alley.

21:39.200 --> 21:42.600
Half of Lin'an… is gone.

21:46.200 --> 21:47.160
What about my sister?

21:48.880 --> 21:50.040
She is alive.

21:50.600 --> 21:52.640
She hurt her leg while fleeing.

21:53.240 --> 21:54.400
She cannot get out of bed.

21:55.000 --> 21:56.840
The doctor says
she might lose her right leg.

21:58.480 --> 21:59.640
She asked me to tell you

22:00.480 --> 22:01.800
she is waiting at home.

22:02.440 --> 22:03.600
Waiting for you to return safely.

22:05.800 --> 22:06.840
Then…

22:07.640 --> 22:09.200
What about… my mother?

22:09.280 --> 22:10.680
She… Is she…

22:14.520 --> 22:16.320
Just say it. What happened to her?

22:17.520 --> 22:18.600
Your mother…

22:21.280 --> 22:22.680
She was so frightened
and suffered a stroke.

22:22.760 --> 22:24.080
She did not make it.

22:29.200 --> 22:31.480
Before she passed,
she told me to tell you,

22:33.160 --> 22:34.960
no matter how hard the days become,

22:35.800 --> 22:37.440
you must keep living.

22:42.680 --> 22:43.760
Mother…

22:46.040 --> 22:46.880
Yuanbao.

22:57.080 --> 22:58.080
And my grandmother?

23:01.080 --> 23:02.400
Grandma Jin is alive.

23:03.120 --> 23:04.200
But

23:04.720 --> 23:06.440
when she fled,

23:06.520 --> 23:07.600
she struck her head.

23:10.960 --> 23:12.640
She remembers nothing now.

23:20.080 --> 23:21.600
Mrs. Zhao is still alive.

23:23.000 --> 23:25.560
Changning and I were separated.

23:26.280 --> 23:27.800
I searched for two months.

23:29.400 --> 23:31.160
I could not find her.

23:34.560 --> 23:35.600
Who did this?

23:36.320 --> 23:37.600
Qingfeng Stronghold.

23:39.600 --> 23:41.680
I killed their second-in-command.

23:42.640 --> 23:44.480
But the one behind it all is still alive.

23:46.880 --> 23:49.760
The heir of Prince Changxin. Sui Yuanqing.

23:52.040 --> 23:54.000
Sui Yuanqing…

23:56.640 --> 23:58.720
What heir?

23:58.800 --> 24:00.480
I will skin him alive.

24:00.560 --> 24:01.800
-Tell me where he is!
-We will.

24:01.880 --> 24:03.320
But not now.

24:04.200 --> 24:05.680
We have other responsibilities.

24:07.200 --> 24:09.520
Bring the surviving people
back to our home in Lin'an.

24:10.080 --> 24:11.240
We should live on.

24:22.160 --> 24:23.400
But

24:23.480 --> 24:25.000
Lin'an is destroyed.

24:26.040 --> 24:27.120
Where is home now?

24:29.000 --> 24:30.600
My father's last wish

24:31.120 --> 24:32.920
was for me to care for my mother.

24:33.520 --> 24:34.960
Now she is gone.

24:35.800 --> 24:37.480
Where do I return to?

24:46.600 --> 24:47.760
Mrs. Zhao lives.

24:48.880 --> 24:50.280
So do the rest

24:50.360 --> 24:52.480
who survived.

24:54.920 --> 24:56.200
As long as we are alive,

24:56.800 --> 24:58.280
Lin'an lives.

24:59.880 --> 25:01.240
Do not lose hope.

25:04.960 --> 25:06.160
Remember this.

25:08.240 --> 25:09.960
We settle this blood debt first.

25:11.400 --> 25:12.560
Then we go home.

25:13.480 --> 25:14.760
-Yes.
-That is right.

25:15.840 --> 25:18.440
Marquis Wu'an has led troops
to wipe out Qingfeng Stronghold.

25:18.520 --> 25:21.520
Justice, at least in part,
has been served.

25:21.600 --> 25:22.960
I swore an oath.

25:24.440 --> 25:25.960
I will bring Changning

25:26.040 --> 25:28.360
and every one of you back safely.

25:28.440 --> 25:29.520
Not a single soul left behind.

25:32.880 --> 25:34.360
As for revenge,

25:34.440 --> 25:35.800
we must plan it carefully.

25:37.800 --> 25:38.640
Understood.

25:48.280 --> 25:49.840
People of Lin'an,

25:51.440 --> 25:52.560
rest well on your final road.

25:53.520 --> 25:54.360
Mother.

25:55.200 --> 25:56.280
Rest well.

25:57.800 --> 25:58.800
Rest well.

26:54.600 --> 26:56.600
Easy. It is only me.

26:59.040 --> 27:01.160
Tao. What are you doing here?

27:01.760 --> 27:04.800
I found a quiet spot upstairs.

27:04.880 --> 27:06.760
Thought I might do a bit of reading.

27:07.480 --> 27:10.600
Did not expect you all
to be hiding here too.

27:13.600 --> 27:14.960
Did we disturb you?

27:16.440 --> 27:17.560
Not at all.

27:18.560 --> 27:20.680
You were snoring quite peacefully.

27:21.280 --> 27:24.000
Your sister is still missing.

27:24.080 --> 27:25.680
The village is in ashes.

27:25.760 --> 27:27.920
You are trapped here.

27:28.000 --> 27:30.680
And yet you sleep so soundly.

27:31.920 --> 27:35.360
Truly fearless through sheer ignorance.

27:36.920 --> 27:38.920
When my parents were alive,
they told me this.

27:39.000 --> 27:41.360
If the sky falls,
someone taller will hold it up.

27:42.360 --> 27:44.040
Whatever happens,

27:44.120 --> 27:45.840
eat well,

27:45.920 --> 27:47.440
sleep well,

27:47.520 --> 27:48.800
live the day in front of you.

27:48.880 --> 27:50.520
To mind one's own peace.

27:53.160 --> 27:55.720
Your parents may not be scholars,

27:57.640 --> 27:59.080
but they are wise in life.

28:00.440 --> 28:02.480
These rascals.

28:02.560 --> 28:04.840
You are close with them?

28:06.480 --> 28:08.880
At first, they came to bully my family.

28:10.200 --> 28:12.200
I beat some manners into them.

28:12.800 --> 28:14.040
Now,

28:14.760 --> 28:15.840
we are like kin.

28:16.440 --> 28:17.920
Beat some manners into them?

28:19.040 --> 28:21.840
You are just like my troublesome disciple.

28:22.440 --> 28:24.720
Stubborn. Proud.

28:26.800 --> 28:29.080
If you were not already married,

28:29.160 --> 28:31.120
you two might have been well matched.

28:31.720 --> 28:33.840
Tao, do not start matchmaking.

28:35.040 --> 28:36.720
My Yan Zheng

28:36.800 --> 28:39.120
is capable and sharp.

28:40.600 --> 28:42.400
Yes, he scowls now and then.

28:43.440 --> 28:44.960
But I happen to like that.

28:47.080 --> 28:48.960
My disciple is no less impressive.

28:49.640 --> 28:51.360
Master of both pen and blade.

28:51.440 --> 28:53.240
Loyal to the core.

28:53.320 --> 28:55.360
In youth, he was too fierce.

28:55.440 --> 28:57.560
I gave him the courtesy name Jiuheng,

28:57.640 --> 29:01.720
so he would weigh every action carefully.

29:02.400 --> 29:05.640
In recent years,
he has not disappointed me.

29:05.720 --> 29:07.760
Though young and already famed,

29:07.840 --> 29:11.280
his composure rivals veteran generals.

29:11.360 --> 29:12.960
And most importantly,

29:13.040 --> 29:15.040
he is striking in appearance.

29:15.120 --> 29:16.920
Graceful as jade.

29:18.040 --> 29:19.320
If we are judging by looks,

29:19.400 --> 29:21.400
my Yan Zheng is unrivaled.

29:25.680 --> 29:26.960
Why do I feel

29:27.040 --> 29:29.240
they are talking about the same person?

29:31.200 --> 29:32.440
Changyu's live-in husband.

29:35.880 --> 29:37.080
Changyu's live-in husband

29:37.160 --> 29:39.720
and Tao's disciple.

29:42.520 --> 29:43.600
That is none of your concern.

29:43.680 --> 29:44.880
Go to sleep.

29:44.960 --> 29:45.800
Sleep.

29:45.880 --> 29:47.720
A live-in son-in-law?

29:52.240 --> 29:54.600
What a pity for my disciple.

29:55.640 --> 29:59.320
Let him remain a bachelor then.

30:02.600 --> 30:03.680
Yan Zheng…

30:15.000 --> 30:16.640
That sneeze means

30:16.720 --> 30:18.760
someone is thinking of you.

30:19.640 --> 30:22.480
Which young maiden

30:22.560 --> 30:24.840
is secretly pining for the Marquis now?

30:25.440 --> 30:27.080
You are insufferable. Go away.

30:35.200 --> 30:37.920
Who first beheld the moon by the river?

30:39.640 --> 30:41.320
In what distant year did that same moon

30:42.440 --> 30:44.000
first shine upon mankind?

31:10.160 --> 31:11.160
Madam.

31:13.880 --> 31:15.360
Do not call me that.

31:16.680 --> 31:18.640
I am nothing but the woman
you pushed into his bed.

31:20.600 --> 31:22.480
I may have made use of you once,

31:22.560 --> 31:24.640
but I bear you no ill will.

31:24.720 --> 31:26.920
You need not see me as an enemy.

31:28.360 --> 31:29.840
We could work together.

31:32.400 --> 31:33.240
Leave.

31:33.320 --> 31:36.760
You'd better accept the fact
of being the Madam here.

31:36.840 --> 31:40.040
Only that can keep the young master alive.

31:40.120 --> 31:41.920
Only then will he have a future.

31:46.560 --> 31:47.440
Bring him in.

31:49.440 --> 31:51.840
-Mother.
-Bao'er.

31:51.920 --> 31:53.000
Mother!

31:53.080 --> 31:54.200
Pretty Lady.

31:57.120 --> 31:58.000
Changning.

32:09.920 --> 32:11.080
Why are you helping me?

32:12.920 --> 32:14.160
What do you want?

32:15.000 --> 32:17.120
Helping you is helping Dayin.

32:18.240 --> 32:20.320
I will keep Young Master safe.

32:20.920 --> 32:23.000
I will safeguard the imperial bloodline.

32:27.720 --> 32:29.800
I only wish for both His Highness

32:29.880 --> 32:31.400
and Young Master to live safely.

32:40.440 --> 32:43.160
-Where are you?
-Right in front of you!

32:43.240 --> 32:44.680
Here!

32:44.760 --> 32:45.880
-Behind you!
-Here?

32:45.960 --> 32:47.880
Behind you, behind you!

32:47.960 --> 32:49.920
-I am here!
-Behind me?

32:50.560 --> 32:52.120
Where did you go? Here?

32:58.600 --> 32:59.720
Caught you!

32:59.800 --> 33:01.560
-I am here!
-Where are you?

33:01.640 --> 33:03.400
-Behind you!
-Careful!

33:03.480 --> 33:04.480
No, that's not right.

33:05.600 --> 33:06.720
Where are you hiding?

33:08.240 --> 33:09.080
Here!

33:10.400 --> 33:11.440
Over here!

33:11.520 --> 33:12.560
Here?

33:12.640 --> 33:14.640
Right here! I am here!

33:15.280 --> 33:16.120
You hid really well.

33:16.920 --> 33:17.880
Where are you?

33:17.960 --> 33:18.960
‎HUMBLE AND REVERENT, KIND AND FORBEARING

33:19.040 --> 33:20.000
Careful, Madam!

33:21.600 --> 33:23.160
So this is what you meant

33:23.240 --> 33:24.160
by a family reunited.

33:25.880 --> 33:26.720
Look at them.

33:27.640 --> 33:29.280
They are truly happy.

33:29.360 --> 33:30.520
I am here!

33:30.600 --> 33:32.200
I can hear your footsteps.

33:35.080 --> 33:36.120
Over here!

33:36.760 --> 33:39.520
One day, I will have this too.

33:39.600 --> 33:41.600
With the one I love and kids

33:43.000 --> 33:44.480
right by my side.

33:48.160 --> 33:49.400
Such a day will come.

33:50.440 --> 33:52.240
-Caught you!
-Mother!

33:56.200 --> 33:57.320
In a moment,

33:57.400 --> 33:58.920
we are going to play a different game.

33:59.920 --> 34:02.320
It is called Forgetting Home.

34:02.400 --> 34:04.160
We feast, we drink, we make merry.

34:04.240 --> 34:05.240
The happier we seem,

34:05.880 --> 34:08.440
the more they will believe
we have given up escaping.

34:08.960 --> 34:10.800
When they lower their guard,

34:10.880 --> 34:12.960
we can actually run away.
Do you understand?

34:16.800 --> 34:18.080
Come. Let us play.

34:22.080 --> 34:23.520
Wave at them. Smile wider.

34:24.719 --> 34:26.159
The brighter you smile,

34:26.239 --> 34:27.679
the sooner you will see Changyu again.

35:12.240 --> 35:13.960
It has been a long time

35:14.040 --> 35:16.080
since I felt something like this.

35:33.960 --> 35:34.960
You are acting it wrong.

35:35.880 --> 35:37.440
Next,

35:38.840 --> 35:40.680
you should take this jade pendant

35:40.760 --> 35:42.320
and fling it at my face.

35:42.920 --> 35:44.080
Say, "Take your reward."

35:48.720 --> 35:49.880
Seven years.

35:59.400 --> 36:01.080
Have there been other men?

36:02.840 --> 36:04.320
Only you.

36:05.320 --> 36:06.360
Liar.

36:19.040 --> 36:20.320
Help!

36:21.600 --> 36:23.000
Fire!

36:23.640 --> 36:24.920
Put it out!

36:29.520 --> 36:31.080
Help!

36:31.640 --> 36:33.400
Help!

37:01.160 --> 37:03.160
Wake up! Wake up!

37:03.240 --> 37:05.360
I arrive here and this is what I find?

37:05.440 --> 37:07.400
Do not die on me.

37:36.920 --> 37:38.400
Good. You are awake.

37:38.480 --> 37:40.760
At least I have done one good deed today.

37:40.840 --> 37:42.880
May the Bodhisattva bless me
to return home soon.

37:51.840 --> 37:54.280
And you, since you survived,

37:54.360 --> 37:55.720
live properly from now on.

37:57.240 --> 37:58.080
I am leaving.

38:12.240 --> 38:13.800
It's you.

38:23.000 --> 38:24.240
Take your reward.

38:34.240 --> 38:35.320
All these years,

38:36.400 --> 38:38.360
have you ever thought of me

38:39.320 --> 38:40.200
in the dead of night?

38:43.160 --> 38:44.000
Yes.

38:45.320 --> 38:46.760
In my nightmares.

38:49.680 --> 38:51.280
Better that than nothing.

39:23.320 --> 39:24.760
By order of the Heir,

39:24.840 --> 39:26.160
the girl is to be taken.

39:26.760 --> 39:29.560
Anyone who disobeys
will be executed on the spot.

39:30.120 --> 39:32.600
Without Master's command,
no one takes her.

39:32.680 --> 39:33.600
You dare defy us?

39:34.920 --> 39:35.760
Try it.

39:37.600 --> 39:38.640
What is this commotion?

39:48.120 --> 39:49.800
Who struck first?

39:50.880 --> 39:52.360
They meant harm to Young Master.

39:52.440 --> 39:53.920
I was forced to act.

39:54.000 --> 39:55.120
Otherwise, Madam would--

39:56.360 --> 39:59.280
Madam? What is a woman worth?

39:59.360 --> 40:00.880
Would you hold up

40:00.960 --> 40:02.520
Yuanqing's grand plan for her sake?

40:03.480 --> 40:04.640
My brother stands at the front,

40:04.720 --> 40:06.040
risking his life.

40:06.120 --> 40:08.920
If my son's life were needed
for the battle, I would not hesitate.

40:09.600 --> 40:12.880
You fools confuse duty with sentiment.
You'll answer under military law!

40:15.400 --> 40:16.560
Yuanhuai!

40:16.640 --> 40:17.480
My brother.

40:18.000 --> 40:20.040
Please calm yourself. Mind your health.

40:20.800 --> 40:22.720
Yuanqing. Why are you here?

40:24.280 --> 40:26.880
My men were incompetent.

40:26.960 --> 40:28.440
Guards. Behead them.

40:29.280 --> 40:30.480
-Yes.
-Hold.

40:31.720 --> 40:32.840
Yuanhuai,

40:32.920 --> 40:34.120
you have me.

40:34.200 --> 40:35.440
There is no need to go so far.

40:37.480 --> 40:39.120
-Stand down.
-Yes.

40:41.760 --> 40:43.400
-Take the girl.
-Yes.

40:43.480 --> 40:44.600
Do not come closer!

40:44.680 --> 40:45.760
Stay back!

40:45.840 --> 40:47.040
Let go of Ning!

40:47.120 --> 40:48.880
-Let go!
-Move!

40:53.320 --> 40:55.640
Ning!

40:56.240 --> 40:57.680
Bao'er!

41:00.880 --> 41:07.840
LUCHENG MILITARY CAMP

41:16.760 --> 41:18.240
So, the mighty Marquis Wu'an

41:18.320 --> 41:21.400
has taken to nibbling sweets like a child?

41:21.480 --> 41:24.280
Is that any of your concern?
Besides, you have none.

41:25.040 --> 41:25.920
None?

41:27.400 --> 41:28.600
If I wished for sweets,

41:28.680 --> 41:31.520
half the noble ladies in the capital
would carry confection shops to my door.

41:33.440 --> 41:35.520
Marquis, a letter
from the Chongzhou army scouts.

41:45.320 --> 41:46.920
This Sui Yuanqing

41:47.000 --> 41:49.600
wants me to exchange Yanzhou
for Changning.

41:53.400 --> 41:55.280
Sui Yuanqing

41:55.360 --> 41:56.560
is getting more arrogant.

42:00.240 --> 42:01.480
Convey my military order.

42:02.080 --> 42:03.840
Have the vanguard battalion
follow me to Baxia.

42:04.480 --> 42:06.120
To bring my daughter

42:06.200 --> 42:07.400
back unharmed.

42:08.000 --> 42:08.920
Yes.

44:50.640 --> 44:53.880
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

44:53.960 --> 44:54.880
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
